    <div class="blog-section">
      <h2>📖 Latest Articles</h2>
      <p style="color:#888;font-size:0.85rem;margin-bottom:1rem;text-align:center;">Educational articles with hands-on activities — written for students, teachers, and parents.</p>
      <div class="blog-list">
        <div class="blog-item">
          <div>
            <div class="b-title">⚛️ Matter Adventures — Solids, Liquids, and Gases Are Everywhere!</div>
            <div class="b-meta">Science · Jun 30, 2026 · 4 min</div>
          </div>
          <a href="/blog/matter-adventures.html" class="b-link">Read →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="blog-item">
          <div>
            <div class="b-title">🏃 Energy Is Everywhere — How a Bouncing Ball Teaches Physics</div>
            <div class="b-meta">Science · Jun 30, 2026 · 4 min</div>
          </div>
          <a href="/blog/energy-everywhere.html" class="b-link">Read →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="blog-item">
          <div>
            <div class="b-title">🌿 Who Eats Who? The Secret Food Web in Your Backyard</div>
            <div class="b-meta">Science · Jun 30, 2026 · 4 min</div>
          </div>
          <a href="/blog/ecosystem-connections.html" class="b-link">Read →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="blog-item">
          <div>
            <div class="b-title">🧩 You Use Algorithms Every Day — You Just Didn't Know It!</div>
            <div class="b-meta">Technology · Jun 30, 2026 · 3 min</div>
          </div>
          <a href="/blog/algorithm-daily-life.html" class="b-link">Read →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="text-align:center;margin-top:1rem;">
        <a href="/blog/" class="btn">📚 View All Articles →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
<footer>
      <p class="phone">📞 <a href="tel:+136****0809">(363) 777-0809</a></p>
      <p>📍 1389 Kearney Ave, Bronx, NY 10465</p>
      <p style="margin-top:0.5rem;">
        <a href="https://mohikontok.com">mohikontok.com</a> · 
        <a href="mailto:soundlab@mohikontok.com">soundlab@mohikontok.com</a>
      </p>
      <p style="margin-top:1rem;">🎧 $65/hr — Soundproof recording, rehearsal & sensory-safe space</p>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
